               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Discourse by John Chrysostom on the Life and Decollation of John the
                     Baptist (fols. 2ra-25vb) 
 II) Commemorative notice from the Sǝnkǝssar on
                     the apparition of the bodies of John the Baptist and Prophet Elijah, for the
                     2nd of Sane (fols. 25vb-29ra)
 III) Homily by John Chrysostom on the glory
                     of John the Baptist (fols. 29ra-45ra) 
 IV) Taʾammǝra Yoḥannǝs Maṭmǝq
                     “Miracles of John the Baptist”: 13 miracles (47ra-71vb), incomplete
 
                     Additio 1.</summary>
